name: 魔力 HIGH Q
content: 当我看着的你来到我身旁
看你每个动作都给我幻想
我的心思忽然飞上了天堂
试图回避啊 你投射的眼光
You make me so high tonight
You make me so q tonight
Like like like like you tonight
Like like like like you tonight
爱 是不是开始发芽
你吐露的气息像晚风一样
哦 你节奏干涸我那么大
身体的海浪不停的拍打
试图回避啊 你燃烧的眼光
You make me so high tonight
You make me so q tonight
You make me so high tonight
You make me so q tonight
Like like like like you tonight
Like like like like you tonight
